                    </div>
                    <span>If Pete Rose was hoping this book would help his case for reinstatement, he has made yet another error.  "My Prison Without Bars" provides insight into Rose's self delusion.  I was ambivalent until reading this book, but Rose convinced me that baseball should never allow him back.  Read it for yourself and I'm certain you will agree. </span>
                  
              
